-- string-length-crystal.cell: trivial crystallization

вҠў measure
  given text вүЎ "pneumonoultramicroscopicsilicovolcanoconiosis"
  yield char-count

  вҲҙ Count the number of characters in В«textВ».

  вҠЁ char-count = 45

вҠў crystallize
  given В§measure
  given measureвҶ’char-count
  yield В§measure', is-faithful

  вҲҙ Read В«В§measureВ». It counts characters.
    Write a вҠў= expression: length(text)

вҠў verify-crystal
  given В§measure'
  given crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful
  given measureвҶ’char-count
  yield approved

  вҲҙ Does В«В§measure'В» produce 45 for the test input?

  вҠЁ if approved and crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful then В§measure' may replace В§measure
